name: the Moon
description: Oil painting created by artist Benicio Gaudino, inspired by the moments. Digitally transformed (1300x820 pixels). Those who buy the NFT will be drawn to the real Screen, in frame. Inspiration: When the moon’s reflection meets the water mirrors, it forms an incredible scene to be observed. It’s a beauty we need to behold at least once in our life. What would our nights be like if we didn’t have the moon? It brightens the darkest nights, makes the stars shine brighter and makes the sky more beautiful and romantic.
